A paragraph with ''emphasis'', '''strong emphasis''', and <code>inline literal</code> text.

A second paragraph that spans two source lines joined by a soft break.

Escapes keep a literal *asterisk* intact, and an inline literal can attach to a word like with<code>code</code> mid-sentence.
